title: #42 - Gloom Reveals the Secrets to YouTube Trending & Meeting Nadeshot at Faze Party
itunes:title: #42 - Gloom Reveals the Secrets to YouTube Trending & Meeting Nadeshot at Faze Party
description: On this remote episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast presented by Cash App, content creator, gamer, and YouTuber Gloom comes onto the show to talk about her favorite video games growing up (Starcraft, Diablo II), meeting Nadeshot at a Faze Party during the 2018 Fortnite Pro Am, how she met Azzyland, collaborating with DrLupo, living in Singapore vs the U.S. & Canada, which Halo was the best in the series, and more!
